sale_listings.description:
Belvoir are pleased to bring to the market a 2 Bedroom apartment, located in the Steele House development in the very popular area of Salford. The property features an open plan living room and kitchen design with modern styling, along with great views

Steele House is situated on the waterside of the River Irwell and is in a fantastic central location connecting you both to Manchester City Centre and Salford. Internally the property comprises of a spacious entrance vestibule with ample storage space, leading directly into the large open plan living room and kitchen. Returning to the entrance hall you will find two double bedrooms with master ensuite and the family bathroom.Â

This apartment also comes with a parking space.

Viewings are highly recommended at this property, please call or email to arrange your viewing.

EPC rating: B. Tenure: Leasehold,

Discover an exceptional opportunity within the prestigious Slater House development. This stylish apartment is perfectly situated between Manchester City Centre and Salford Quays, offering the best of urban living.

Mortgage buyers are welcome, thanks to recent amendments in lending criteria following the Building Safety Act 2022. Full funding from the developer is in place.

Conveniently located near major public transport links and local amenities, this spacious fourth-floor apartment features an open-plan living area with a Juliet balcony, a modern kitchen, two double bedrooms, an en-suite master bedroom, and a main three-piece bathroom suite.

Additional benefits include secure allocated parking.
